name: Sacrifice, 2016
description: An expanse somewhere in the American West. Each buyer of the initial edition of 25 will receive an 11x14” archival pigment print, signed and numbered, on Hahnemühle Photo Rag Baryta. Please contact me via Twitter or IG (@codycobb) to arrange shipping. 20% of each sale will be donated to The Nature Conservancy (www.nature.org) and directed to support causes in Utah.
